    "data": [
        {
            "title": "美國銀行業將在巴塞爾計畫中面臨新的抵押貸款資本要求",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 隨著聯儲會進一步接近公佈與巴塞爾協議III相關的銀行資本提案，美國貸款機構料將面臨新的住房<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:抵押貸款;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/抵押貸款\">抵押貸款</a>要求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會負責銀行監管的最高官員米歇爾·鮑曼表示，這項新措施中涉及住宅房地產的部分，將考慮提高銀行賬面上抵押貸款資本要求的「風險敏感度」。一種方法是根據貸款價值比來確定住宅房地產風險敞口的適用風險權重，而非採用統一的風險權重。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這一變化可以使資本要求與實際風險更好地匹配，支持銀行的資產負債表內貸款，並有可能逆轉過去15年來抵押貸款活動向非銀機構遷移的趨勢，」鮑曼周一在為美國銀行家協會佛羅里達州活動準備的發言稿中表示。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ce053320-ee44-31a1-84e7-73e072b70e90-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博新聞社此前報導，川普時代的監管機構正在在制定一項新的銀行資本提案，該提案對美國最大銀行造成的負擔將小於拜登時代的計畫。早先的方案中包含一些更嚴格的抵押貸款資本要求，面對銀行業的強烈反對，最終未能定稿。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：聯儲會據悉醞釀新規 擬大幅放寬大型銀行的資本金上調要求</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鮑曼周一還表示，監管機構將就某些抵押貸款相關的風險權重徵求意見。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「通過創建一個具有韌性的抵押貸款市場，讓各類金融機構積極參與其中，無論經濟狀況如何，我們都能為借款人提供負擔得起的信貸和高質量的服務。加強銀行參與這些活動並不會威脅到銀行體系的安全與穩健，」鮑曼周一表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Banks to See New Mortgage Capital Requirements in Basel Plan</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E5%B0%87%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%B4%E5%A1%9E%E7%88%BE%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E4%B8%AD%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-145654556.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 23:34:38",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利調整歐洲投資銀行業務領導層",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 摩根士丹利對歐洲投資銀行業務領導層進行了一系列調整，此舉正值該地區併購活動料將出現激增之際。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博新聞社看到的內部備忘錄顯示，這家美國銀行任命William Bertagna擔任歐洲、中東和非洲地區投資銀行業務副主管。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bertagna將接替Martin Grebner的職位，後者與Markus Fimpel共同獲選執掌該行歐洲、中東和非洲地區工業組。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前領導該地區工業組的Karsten Hofacker將轉任歐洲、中東和非洲地區金融保薦人併購業務主管。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-369f6f26-592d-3bec-b77b-24c1be23667b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利發言人證實了備忘錄內容。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Morgan Stanley Shuffles Investment Banking Leaders in Europe (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E9%A0%98%E5%B0%8E%E5%B1%A4-124940262.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 22:08:08",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "法國對提升歐元國際地位的努力有所顧慮 呼籲評估相關經濟風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 法國政府對歐洲尋求加強歐元國際地位的努力有所顧慮，呼籲評估相關經濟風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:歐元區;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐元區\">歐元區</a>財長將於周一晚些時候在布魯塞爾會面，討論如何在發行與交易中促進歐元的使用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一名法國財政部官員匿名向記者吹風時表示，巴黎支持這項努力，但希望更深入地了解：如果該舉措進一步推高歐元兌美元匯率，出口商將為此付出怎樣的代價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國歷來是提升歐元在全球經濟中分量的積極支持者，也經常抱怨美元的主導地位。相關情緒最早可追溯至20世紀60年代，當時法國前總統Valery Giscard D’Estaing提出「過度特權」一詞，用以形容美元享有的特殊地位。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7d951872-f2e7-3d3a-8738-45487d886464-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，這名法國官員表示，歐元區經濟如今未必能夠復制這種特權，部分原因在於歐元區對世界其他地區存在貿易順差。該人士稱，如果在危機時刻歐元成為投資者的避險資產，歐元區出口商將同時遭受兩重打擊：經濟下行時需求的下降，以及歐元的升值。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題France Sees Reasons for Caution on Bolstering Euro’s Global Role</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B%E6%9C%89%E6%89%80%E9%A1%A7%E6%85%AE-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%A9%95%E4%BC%B0%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-143141552.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 23:34:39",
