            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "伊朗外長與國際原子能機構總幹事舉行會談 美伊新一輪談判即將展開",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 伊朗外長阿巴斯·阿拉格齊周一在日內瓦與聯合國原子能機構負責人舉行會談，為即將與美國展開的第二輪核談判做準備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:伊朗國家電視台;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/伊朗國家電視台\">伊朗國家電視台</a>報導稱，阿拉格齊在與國際原子能機構總幹事拉斐爾·馬裡亞諾·格羅西會談時，討論了將於周二與美國特使史蒂夫·威特科夫進行的間接會談中將提出的「方案」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國務卿馬爾科·盧比奧向記者表示，他對德黑蘭與華盛頓能克服多年緊張對峙與敵意、最終達成協議「抱有希望」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「與伊朗達成實質性協議向來困難重重，因為我們面對的是依據神學而非地緣政治決策的激進神職人員。但且看事態發展，我希望談判能成功，我們都希望如此。」盧比奧說。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-02cab32a-7068-3f1e-a7a7-3a1f27c02359-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·川普曾威脅稱，除非伊朗同意達成限制其核計畫的協議以換取制裁解除，否則將對伊朗發動打擊。針對伊朗政權近期鎮壓大規模抗議活動並造成人員死亡，川普已在伊朗附近調集了軍艦和戰鬥機。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：油價波動 伊朗在美伊新一輪會談前舉行演練</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據伊朗半官方塔斯尼姆通訊社報導，伊朗伊斯蘭革命衛隊周一在霍爾木茲海峽附近舉行演練。這凸顯出石油資源豐富的波斯灣地區緊張局勢持續升溫。報導稱，演練涉及對該戰略性航道的「智能控制」，演練重點關注對潛在安全威脅作出「快速、果斷且全面的反應」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普的女婿賈裡德·庫什納預計將於周二與威特科夫共同率領美國代表團參與會談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Iran Meets UN Nuclear Chief Before Next Round of US Talks (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jonathan Tirone、Eric Martin.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E8%88%87%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E8%83%BD%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%B8%BD%E5%B9%B9%E4%BA%8B%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E8%AB%87-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%B0-%E8%BC%AA%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B-141942452.html",
