        {
            "title": "高盛稱英國國債將無視政治風險 2026年有望表現強勁",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"645\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iltb.WvPgSkTeca5G3JZKg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/53070ec7aa691b8dd5d7502ec66a725c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 高盛策略師預測，受英國央行降息推動，2026年英國國債將上漲，政府借貸成本將降至2024年以來最低水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行歐洲高級市場策略師George Cole表示，基準10年期英國國債殖利率預計將到今年底達到4%。他認為，40個基點的降幅基於通膨回落促使英央行採取行動，其影響將蓋過政治風險引發的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Cole在致客戶報告中稱，「儘管英國風險溢價和政治不確定性可能在即將舉行的地方選舉期間持續居高不下，但我們認為有利的宏觀環境將推動國債殖利率走低。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-08e2e6bb-c26c-3c7a-858e-a0d84395a0e8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於頑固通膨使英國央行決策者在降息方面保持謹慎，英國的借貸成本高於其他國家。投資者還擔心該國的財政狀況，本月早些時候，由於首相基爾·斯塔默面臨被迫下台的風險，而潛在接替者可能會尋求更多借款，英國國債殖利率一度飆升。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"645\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nkf06uHTzK72zlXecS0cWA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3716fb8c6f6ec1230e06119b5134ab2f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Cole表示，隨著5月地方選舉臨近，政治不確定性持續存在，預計斯塔默領導的工黨將表現不佳，這可能使風險溢價維持在較高水平。不過，他指出，這些波動平均僅推動債券殖利率上升30個基點，且此類波動通常持續時間較短。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國政府面臨的嚴格財政約束同樣緩解了政治風險。Cole指出，這「最終限制了潛在政府更迭中政策波動的幅度」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">宏觀不確定性降低與通膨回落趨勢加劇正為英國國債提供支撐，這種前景促使貨幣市場消化2026年英國央行降息近兩次的預期。Cole建議買入英國國債，同時賣出德國國債。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman Says Gilts to Look Past Political Risk in Strong 2026</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E7%A8%B1%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E5%B0%87%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-2026%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81-114520663.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 20:36:47",
