        {
            "title": "盧比奧稱匈牙利總理歐爾班連任符合美國利益 願在必要時提供金融協助",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Akos Stiller/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HE.szfFfB51oE9U61DGafA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/dc20600d9f775ed2a642b8e9bb0f3e98\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Akos Stiller/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國國務卿馬爾科·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:盧比奧;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/盧比奧\">盧比奧</a>在布達佩斯與匈牙利總理<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:歐爾班;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐爾班\">歐爾班</a>·維克多舉行聯合記者會時表示，如果匈牙利出現任何金融困難，美國總統唐納德·川普將準備好提供協助。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">盧比奧在匈牙利4月選戰進入最後衝刺階段之際發表此番講話，並暗示，川普致力於歐爾班取得成功，並稱歐爾班連任符合美國的國家利益。 </p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Akos Stiller/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/65m7W.fLrSFrPrwDU2sEXQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8057ca8075b6f2d8d918f47f14c231ff\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Akos Stiller/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐爾班去年訪問白宮後曾表示，他收到了川普提供「金融盾牌」的提議。盧比奧的上述表態似乎是迄今為止最為明確的確認，即如有需要，美國準備好提供這一支持。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-aae33be3-4a13-3260-adbf-946b00d659eb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐爾班在民調中仍落後於Peter Magyar的蒂薩黨(Tisza），Magyar曾是執政黨青年民主主義者聯盟(Fidesz)的成員。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我可以很有把握地告訴你，川普總統深深致力於你的成功，因為你的成功就是我們的成功，」盧比奧說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Rubio Pledges US Support for Hungary’s Orban Ahead of Tight Vote</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Thomas Escritt.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9B%A7%E6%AF%94%E5%A5%A7%E7%A8%B1%E5%8C%88%E7%89%99%E5%88%A9%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E6%AD%90%E7%88%BE%E7%8F%AD%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A-%E9%A1%98%E5%9C%A8%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E6%99%82%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9-114300497.html",
